---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contribute" path="/contribute" pageWidth="wide" pageClass="pt-10">
  <article class="rm-prose max-w-[48rem]">
    <h1>Contribute</h1>
    <p>
      rightmodel improves when the ruleset and task archetypes improve. If you have a better signal
      pattern, a missing task page or a wrong recommendation to report, the repo is the right place
      to do it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Start with the <a href="https://github.com/rightmodel/web/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">contribution guide</a>,
      the content schemas in <code>src/content/config.ts</code> and the task files in <code>src/content/tasks</code>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Issue templates live in <a href="https://github.com/rightmodel/web/issues">GitHub Issues</a>.
      Every contribution is reviewed before merging.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
